  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1635920/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1763390006\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1635920/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1763390006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1635920/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1763390006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1635920/extras/88ebf988bd6d473d25e84b231e74d7fa.avif?t=1763390006\" width=610 height=193 /></span><br>A dog named Mato is a brave dog in an inverted world where you need to solve puzzles by rotating and walking on walls and ceilings.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1635920/extras/98e4e9db1ea350e98b6378fdd3b1c8f5.poster.avif?t=1763390006\" width=594 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1635920/extras/98e4e9db1ea350e98b6378fdd3b1c8f5.webm?t=1763390006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1635920/extras/98e4e9db1ea350e98b6378fdd3b1c8f5.mp4?t=1763390006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features of the game:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Mato loves to run and bark.<br></li><li>Mato barks and jumps.<br></li><li>Mato can rotate the level.<br></li><li>Mato can switch levers.<br></li><li>Mato can teleport.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1635920/extras/88ebf988bd6d473d25e84b231e74d7fa.avif?t=1763390006\" width=610 height=193 /></span><br>A dog named Mato is a brave dog in an inverted world where you need to solve puzzles by rotating and walking on walls and ceilings.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1635920/extras/98e4e9db1ea350e98b6378fdd3b1c8f5.poster.avif?t=1763390006\" width=594 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1635920/extras/98e4e9db1ea350e98b6378fdd3b1c8f5.webm?t=1763390006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1635920/extras/98e4e9db1ea350e98b6378fdd3b1c8f5.mp4?t=1763390006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features of the game:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Mato loves to run and bark.<br></li><li>Mato barks and jumps.<br></li><li>Mato can rotate the level.<br></li><li>Mato can switch levers.<br></li><li>Mato can teleport.</li></ul>",
